  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Instalao de LXTask</title>



    <!--
    <para>

      First, fix some <quote>multiple definition</quote> issues exposed
      by GCC-10:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>patch -Np1 -i ../lxtask-&lxtask-version;-gcc10_fix-1.patch</userinput></screen>
-->
<para>
      Instale <application>LXTask</application> executando os seguintes comandos:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Esse pacote no vem com uma sute de teste.
    </para>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usurio(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

